outputs.output_descr: The RTP project aims to ensure Government's leadership in coordinating aid at macro, sectoral and cross sectoral level; increase aid transparency, predictability, and integration of planning and budgeting framework; and enhance aid effectiveness and impact on development.

project_descr: Enriching the Round Table Process for Increased Aid Effectiveness and Development Results
project_title: Enriching the RTP for Increased Aid Effect. & Dev. Resul
